{"type": "article", "id": 7586, "title": "Stratasys 3D 打印椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-20T07:32:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234802WS84yfcJoGrZdmvQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t洛杉矶设计建筑工作室 Synthesis Design + Architecture 受 Stratasys 公司委托，设计了这一款 3D 打印椅子，采用的室最先进的梯度3D打印技术。Stratasys 要求工作者设计的椅子离开了 3D 技术便无法完成，而工作室最终完成的这件作品达到的更高标准是：离开了 Stratasys 的 Objet 500 Connex3 技术便无法完成。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234800KHeJ48NPjolEGpFW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66603774\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234800e9Si2EU5nbKsAqPx.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66603774\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348006p2we0BNQAJvOI8Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66603774\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234801H6Tm8kEp5J4fYd7j.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64528302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}